primary.context: Caller received a letter about the new portal but is struggling with the ID and registration process
primary.detail: The agent explained the difference between RCI and Vacatia IDs and confirmed the email address to send a new registration link.

steps: Caller explained difficulty registering for the new Clubhouse portal.
Agent performed account lookup and identity verification.
Agent clarified that RCI ID is not the same as Vacatia ID.
Agent explained that the Vacatia ID is generated after registration.
Agent confirmed the caller's email address to send a new registration link.

clarifications.note: Agent asked for last name spelling again

corrections.note: User corrected agent's spelling of last name

actions.detail: Verified name and state of residence
Confirmed email to send registration link

insights.summary: The caller was confused by the registration requirements for the new Vacatia Clubhouse portal, specifically regarding the ID number. The agent successfully verified the account, explained the ID discrepancy, and prepared to send a registration link.
insights.verbatim: I type in the code that I got from the code, and it says it's not no good. Actually, it logged me in. It says we're already we're already members. I'm just trying to set this thing up. It's ridiculous.
